additionalInfo.description:
This function checks if the values of the column are valid boolean or not.

Arguments:
column: [string] Column name on which the check is to be applied.
boolValue1: [string] Valid boolean value 1 for the column
boolValue2: [string] Valid boolean value 2 for the column

Return Type: 
[Numeric] Returns 0 for invalid rows and 1 for valid rows.
